{
  "text": "*Average blood concentrations of C4, C4d, C5a, and CYFRA in lung cancer patients were obtained from previous reports [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Total protein in blood was calculated in our laboratory using 134 plasma samples from lung cancer patients. **Calculated as the ratio of the marker in BAL fluids divided by the ratio of the marker in blood.",
